project_descr: Apoio às Políticas Públicas de Desenvolvimento Sustentável

outputs.output_descr: The Project "Support Public Policies for Sustainable Development", BRA/00/022 aims to participate in the efforts of the Ministry of Environment to prepare instruments for environmental management and sustainable rural development for the benefit of the environmental and life quality in Brazil.
